{
  "stem": "5761.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But I-- it bothered me till 1950, when I came to United States and they cured it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But I remember was-- this was our contribution to the family, go stay in line, you know, for foo, and go to the forest and cut logs to make a fire in the house to keep warm.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Never went to school there and tried to be as helpful as I could.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody has a part [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and did it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But again, we did not have adequate, you know, clothing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My older sister used to know how to, to sew, you know, on a sewing machine.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She took blankets.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she make boots out of blankets and really saved a lot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You didn't freeze in your legs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And whatever anybody could participate in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] good memories, we did not have there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because one day, they arrested my father and accused him being a counter revolutionary in the camp, saying that he had seen Russian youth, Communist youth, singing songs.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he went over and he hit them, told them to stop, otherwise he's going to hit them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This was his accusation.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Naturally, arrested him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they took him to Sverdlovsk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And he was indicted to be executed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But again, the whole family got together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we thought, what can we do to help him?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Naturally, my older sister and then my older brothers [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] went to Sverdlovsk.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we bribed the commander of the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he made the arrangements we should go to Sverdlovsk.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Same time, we got a connection of the head of the jail and the judge and big officials.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
